	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Hey folks.  It's been a while, but I figured I'd make a new post rather than digging up that old one.
<br />
<br />Anyway, the game has a title now.  It is "Battle Kid:  Fortress of Peril".  It took a few days on another forum to finally settle on a title, but I'm glad that's decided.
<br />
<br />Other news, I've got around 425 or so rooms, 35 enemies, and 4 bosses in and will be working on more bosses soon.  Hoping to have 8 total bosses.
<br />
<br />I made a third video and talked about some things.  This video is a little old, but I figured I'd post it:
<br /><a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BJGEknTXZio" class="postlink">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BJGEknTXZio</a>
<br />
<br />Other than that, things are progressing and I'm hoping to be done by summer.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


