		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle">Celius wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">I like that you can re-use the same checkpoints. Will you be enforcing a life system with limited continues or anything like that?</div>
<br />
<br />Hi, actually yes.  I was planning to have 4 difficulty settings:
<br />
<br />Normal:  Infinite continues and has a password feature
<br />Hard:  No passwords (true for the rest), 50 continues.  Obviously must be done in one sitting
<br />Very hard:  15 continues
<br />Unfair:  Death = back to the title screen.   <img src="./images/smilies/icon_cool.gif" alt="8)" title="Cool" />

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


