		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />For saving, using Flash instead of EPROM would be cheaper than a battery.  But then you need a bit to select between mapper writes and memory writes (or decode the mapper somewhere else).
<br />
<br />Passwords seem OK though.

		

		</td>
